    All tables should be wrapped in a <span><code class="hljs"><span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">div</span> <span class="hljs-attr">class</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;table-wrapper&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span></code></span> element 
