    and with banded columns and banded rows.
    <br>
    All table cells have a relative position, so you can add absolutely positioned buttons to them for a Rich Text Editor.
    <br>
    <span class="t-info fw-regular">
      The decision was made to not make the table responsive given that the presentation of the data is more important than the presentation of the entire table.
    </span>
  </div>

</details>
